| UI Framework   | React 18             | Required by syllabus                     |
| Language       | TypeScript           | Required by syllabus — type safety       |
| Build Tool     | Vite                 | Fastest, modern — replaces Create React App |
| Routing        | React Router DOM v6  | Industry standard for React routing      |
| State          | React Context API    | Syllabus requires Context API            |
