## 10. Phase-by-Phase Build Plan

### Phase 1 — Setup (Day 1)
- Create new folder careerlens-react
- Run Vite setup command with React + TypeScript template
- Install React Router DOM
- Copy all 8 CSS files into src/assets/css/
- Set up tsconfig.json
- Confirm blank app runs on localhost:5173

### Phase 2 — Types and Context (Day 1)
- Create src/types/index.ts with all interfaces
- Create src/context/AuthContext.tsx
- Create src/context/AnalysisContext.tsx
- Create src/utils/roleSkills.ts
- Create src/utils/helpers.ts

### Phase 3 — Shared Components (Day 2)
- Build Navbar.tsx
- Build Sidebar.tsx
- Build Topbar.tsx
- Build Footer.tsx
- Build ProtectedRoute.tsx
- Set up App.tsx with all routes

### Phase 4 — Auth Pages (Day 2-3)
- Build Login.tsx
- Build Register.tsx
- Build ForgotPassword.tsx
- Wire up AuthContext login and register functions
- Test: login works, token stored, redirect to dashboard

### Phase 5 — Landing Page (Day 3)
- Build Landing.tsx with all sections
- Hero, preview card, stats, steps, features, footer

### Phase 6 — Dashboard (Day 4)
- Build StatCard.tsx, ScoreRing.tsx, SkillBar.tsx, ScoreChart.tsx
- Build Dashboard.tsx using all components
- Test: shows correctly after login

### Phase 7 — Analyse Flow (Day 5-6)
- Build RoleCard.tsx, StepBar.tsx, UploadZone.tsx
- Build Analyse.tsx (role selection)
- Build Upload.tsx (file upload)
- Build LoadingScreen.tsx (animated progress)
- Build Results.tsx with SkillTag and SuggestionItem
- Test: full flow works end to end

### Phase 8 — Inner Pages (Day 7)
- Build Insights.tsx
- Build Skills.tsx
- Build Careers.tsx
- Build History.tsx

### Phase 9 — Account Pages (Day 8)
- Build Profile.tsx
- Build Settings.tsx
- Build Notifications.tsx

### Phase 10 — Extra Pages (Day 8)
- Build Terms.tsx
- Build NotFound.tsx

### Phase 11 — Polish and Deploy (Day 9)
- Fix any routing or state bugs
- Test every page and flow
- Deploy to Netlify

