## Key Differences: Old Project vs React Project

| Topic | Old HTML Project | New React Project |
|-------|-----------------|-------------------|
| Language | HTML + JS | TypeScript (TSX) |
| Pages | 18 .html files | 18 .tsx components |
| Routing | Browser file paths | React Router DOM |
| State | sessionStorage + DOM | useState + Context |
| Auth guard | requireAuth() in every JS file | ProtectedRoute component |
| CSS | Linked in each HTML head | Imported in each component |
| Forms | document.getElementById | useState controlled inputs |
| Navigation | window.location.href | useNavigate() hook |
| Reusable UI | Copy-paste HTML blocks | Reusable components |
| Type safety | None | Full TypeScript |

